title: Three Policies in 5th Economic Package (Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia)
text: ( Source : Ministry of Finance of the Republic of Indonesia ) Jakarta , 23/10/ 2015 MoF - Government has issued the Fifth Economic Policy Package on Thursday (22/10). It emphasizes on three policies of deregulation, namely asset revaluation,
